    This programm is shareware.

          This is a unregistrated version of the software.
          It is not ready but it is a beta version so you
          can see how fast the scanner works with scsi and
          how it works in 24 bit on the Retina. I made this
          software so I can use this scanner.



          *** I use a pretty big screen 1024 x 768 ***

          *** Use cycle 2 menu, it is pretty handy ***

          *** I add a picture with a 24 bit scan   ***

