@node 1 "Installation"

    Installation
    ============

    Copy the software on youre harddisk

    With icon-information you can set the unit number.
    Default is unit 3.


       
    @{"    index    " link index}

@endnode


@node 2 "Buttons"

    Buttons
    =======

    Save                       Save a picture in 24 bit

    Cancel                     Cancel the operation (not 100 %) soon

    Preview                    A quick 256 gray scan.

    Scan                       Scan the image 24 bit. It scans the area
                               you have select.

    Dpi                        Set the dpi of the scanner. It sets the
                               X and Y dpi. Maybe I spit this.
                               (use cycle to menu). If you go to a lower
                               DPI you must reset de area Reste button.
                               else you get a scsi error (sense).
                               DPI go from 50 to 600 dpi.

    Zoom                       Same as dpi. You can set 50 to 200 zoom.
                               It set X and Y. Maybe I spit this.

    Set                        You can draw a rectangle on the screen.
                               This rectangle is the scanned area.
                               If you set X lager than the max area
                               you get a sense error. (Working on it)

    Reset                      Set the area to the max resolution.

    x1,y1,x2,y2                This is the scanned area. You can edit
                               manuel.

    Cycle button 256/24        Yet only 24 bit. Soon it wil work.

    Sharp                      You can set a sharper image or not.

    Speed                      Hi speed scan or slow speed.

    Gamma correction.          You can set the gammacorrection insite
                               the scanner.

    Color                      It only works in Colormode. Soon you can
                               drop R, G or B and you can scan monochrome.

    Bright                     This set a brighter image or not.

    Halftone                   You can set some dither modes. This does
                               not work in 24 bit.

    ColorCorrection            If you scan to a printer than you can correct
                               the color. (not suported)


    
    @{"    index    " link index}

@endnode

